settings.description: The first level from Super Mario Flash.
A partial recreation of 8-4 from Super Mario Bros.
Careful, these creepy crawling beetles just love roaming around on all these wooden walkways! think you can find their hidden Tanooki suit though?
The sewers have been filled with water, possibly too much to handle for Mario.
watch out! while there may be some nice treasure at the end, you'll need to use some lavaproof beachballs to cross through this dangerous pipeline!
Mario wakes up late because his youtube channel left him 5 years ago, you will have less than 8 seconds to run quite fast, put it to the test
with a boatload of bullets! honestly love how the four way bullet bill generators exist, for they're such an underused feature found originally in super mario world.

Just keep running, and don't stop! Let the triangular blocks guide you!
Difficulty: 2/5
Galoombas walk around in their peaceful hills, with lots of sandy and thin structures.
